.SH NAME
qla4xxx_wait_login_resp_boot_tgt \- Wait for iSCSI boot target login response.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" qla4xxx_wait_login_resp_boot_tgt
.BI "(struct scsi_qla_host *ha "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ha" 12
pointer to adapter structure
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
When the boot entry is normal iSCSI target then DF_BOOT_TGT flag will be
set in DDB and we will wait for login response of boot targets during
probe.
